  <md:title>Crime and the Law</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you should be able to:</para><list>
<item>Identify and differentiate between different types of crimes</item>
<item>Evaluate U.S. crime statistics</item>
<item>Understand the three branches of the U.S. criminal justice system</item>
</list></md:abstract>
