        <section id="fs-id2316419" class="further-research" type="further-research">
        <title>Further Research</title>
        <para id="import-auto-id1111554">Is the U.S. criminal justice system confusing? You’re not alone. Check out this handy <link url="http://openstax.org/l/US_Criminal_Justice_BJS" window="new">flowchart from the Bureau of Justice Statistics</link>.</para>
<para id="import-auto-id1967457">How is crime data collected in the United States? Read about the methods of data collection and take the <link url="http://openstax.org/l/Victimization_Survey" window="new">National Crime Victimization Survey</link>.</para>
</section>
